@NODE Introduction
@TITLE "AntiWordGUI À Introduction"


    @{b}Introduction@{ub}


 Some people don't want use shell , they need GUI for programs.

 That's why AntiWordGUI was been created.
    

@ENDNODE

@NODE Requirements
@TITLE "AntiWordGUI À Requirements"


    @{b}Requirements@{ub}


    - MorphOS               (+MUI)
    - AmigaOS 3.x or higher (+MUI)
    - datatypes in both versions

@ENDNODE

@NODE Installation
@TITLE "AntiWordGUI À Installation"


    @{b}Installation@{ub}


    Copy AntiWordGUI to a place where you have AntiWord.

@ENDNODE

@NODE Commandline
@TITLE "MiniShowPicture À Commandline"


    @{b}CLI options@{ub}


    FILE "path/file"

    you can show picture after start program.

    DIR "path"

    you can also select viewed dir after program start.


@ENDNODE



